Hi there! I'd be happy to help you create a plot that compares two columns in a pandas DataFrame.

To start, can you tell me a bit more about the DataFrame you have? What are the column names and what kind of data do they contain? Additionally, what type of plot are you looking to create (e.g. line plot, bar chart, scatter plot)? Knowing this information will help me provide you with more tailored guidance.
